pullRequest.bodyText:
This sample was previously waiting for two issues to be fixed for the LOCK_RASTER method. I've set the target branch to dev so that the lock raster method will work correctly when the sample is publicly released.
Currently, the mapView is instantiated and the DrawStatusChangedListener set before the map is created so that COMPLETED draw status events will be generated and the progress indicator can be used, as advised by the Java team.
@jenmerritt I have added the new SS7 URL for the image raster service.
Thanks!
@JonLavi

